The Wrangler and its 4-door sibling, the Wrangler Unlimited, come in four trim levels for 2015, all with a 3.6L V6 engine. The engine makes 285 hp at 5,200 rpm and 260 lb-ft of torque. All Wrangler models have a 6-speed manual transmission as standard equipment, while a 5-speed automatic is optional.

This used Grand Wagoneer lets you cart everyone, and everything you need in one vehicle, all while transporting in comfort with many added amenities. With a pristine exterior, and a very well-maintained interior, which is in excellent condition, this Jeep is one beautiful vehicle!
